#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:86
msgid "configuring"
msgstr "configurando"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><indexterm><primary>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:90
msgid "/etc/udev/rules.d/65-kvm.rules"
msgstr "/etc/udev/rules.d/65-kvm.rules"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:94
msgid ""
"The default udev rule installed by Eudev would allow all users to access "
"<filename class='devicefile'>/dev/kvm</filename>.  The editors consider it "
"dangerous.  Create a configuration file to override it:"
msgstr ""
"A regra padrão do Udev instalada pelo Eudev permitiria que todos(as) os(as) "
"usuários(as) acessassem <filename class='devicefile'>/dev/kvm</filename>. "
"Os(As) editores(as) consideram perigoso. Crie um arquivo de configuração "
"para substituí-lo:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:99
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">cat > /etc/udev/rules.d/65-kvm.rules &lt;&lt; \"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>KERNEL==\"kvm\", GROUP=\"kvm\", MODE=\"0660\", TAG+=\"uaccess\"</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">cat > /etc/udev/rules.d/65-kvm.rules &lt;&lt; "
"\"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>KERNEL==\"kvm\", GROUP=\"kvm\", MODE=\"0660\", TAG+=\"uaccess\""
"</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><indexterm><primary>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:104
msgid "/etc/udev/hwdb.bin"
msgstr "/etc/udev/hwdb.bin"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:107
msgid ""
"Information about hardware devices is maintained in the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/etc/udev/hwdb.d</filename> and <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/lib/udev/hwdb.d</filename> directories.  "
"<application>Eudev</application> needs that information to be compiled into "
"a binary database <filename>/etc/udev/hwdb.bin</filename>. Create the "
"initial database:"
msgstr ""
"Informação acerca de dispositivos de hardware é mantida nos diretórios "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/etc/udev/hwdb.d</filename> e <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/lib/udev/hwdb.d</filename>. <application>Eudev</"
"application> precisa que a informação seja compilada em uma base de dados "
"binária <filename>/etc/udev/hwdb.bin</filename>. Crie a base de dados "
"inicial:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>udevadm hwdb --update</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>udevadm hwdb --update</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/eudev.xml:116
msgid ""
"This command needs to be run each time the hardware information is updated."
msgstr ""
"Esse comando precisa ser executado cada vez que a informação de hardware for "
"atualizada."

